all_attribute_frames.description: Adds +1 to ATK, making it easier to land hits with this weapon category
Adds +1 to PWR, making your weapons in this category hit hard
Adds +1 to DEF, making it easier to dodge hits with this weapon category
Adds +1 to PRT, making your weapons in this category absorb blows easier

This unit receives an ATK boost for each time they loop past the end of their Itinerary, without returning to base.

Boost begins the first time they have looped once.

By focusing on the battle at hand, this unit gains PWR as the battle rages on.

Applies a PWR debuff that quickly turns into a buff.

This unit rarely gets caught off guard, and leads their Ensemble with their head on a swivel.

Their Ensemble gets ambushed less often with Gathering, but when they do, it's more dangerous.

This unit knows the lands, they are able to move quickly through the wilds.

Their Ensemble can entirely skip Travelling steps of their Itineraries, getting more done, but getting less downtime.

This unit increases in Power as its allies take damage.

Each time its allies take damage during a battle, its Power increases.
